Margie Liszt https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Margie_Liszt 0 Margie Liszt (March 2, 1909 – August 24, 1992) was an American actress. She made 37 television and movie appearances, including I Love Lucy and several Three Stooges films. She died of colon cancer at the age of 83 at Laguna Hills, California.
